      "orig": "My home internet comes from Spectrum (formerly Time Warner Cable) and they offer IPv6 addresses for cable modem subscribers. One of the handy features they provide is  DHCPv6 prefix delegation . If you're not familiar with that topic, here's a primer on how you get IPv6 addresses:",
